{"tid":621349,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人留意今年嘅潑水節？","createTime":"2018-04-08T08:49:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T18:54:23.000Z","uid":101935,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2bb9348534af58bd2bab2704fe31d6333a5425b1","tid":621349,"uid":101935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T08:49:48.000Z","msg":"印象中每年香港都會喺九龍城搞個潑水節，封幾條街然後啲人就拎住水槍周圍射下巡遊下，之前幾年都有去，的確幾好氣氛。<br />\n<br />\n直到今年四月頭，開始見到九龍城出現呢啲宣傳，ig，yahoo周圍都睇到。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/08/161429_1dfd3fe3c8a213fac51c074b57766522.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F08%2F161429_1dfd3fe3c8a213fac51c074b57766522.png&h=7145b611&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當刻覺得有啲商業化，心諗咁奇怪泰國野唔去九龍城但去荔枝角？但最後今日都去睇下係點啦，對佢都仲有少少期望。<br />\n<br />\n一出D2，聽到音樂都好似幾有氣氛，諗住都ok啦應該。<br />\n<br />\n點知，嘩屌。<br />\n劃咗個乜撚野「激戰區」，啲人就喺入面射下水，完全無咗九龍城有得周街走跑來跑去射人嗰種感覺，圍住個框大家射下水，我點解唔去沙灘？得個框咁比我，而家敷衍定施捨？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/08/162905_04d0cb086a2fd95eebcaacae1455fd8b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F08%2F162905_04d0cb086a2fd95eebcaacae1455fd8b.png&h=4ffc3234&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦唔緊要，即管就去睇下佢個泰國市集有幾把炮。上到去個乜鳩d2 place，再屌多聲。完全係拎左個潑水節嚟比商家佬發個財。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一個叫做有特式少少既活動都搞到咁，成個活動最特別係可以喺條街射下水，而家是鳩但劃個框比你滿足下你就將大半個重點放去市集賺你錢，香港真係無撚得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"133f201c74330b6d6fac97c4dcaf881d1ec0b060","tid":621349,"uid":101935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T08:54:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61e6ca2ccf8992de85553d2362717d8a42d83566","tid":621349,"uid":101935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T08:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf1cf8cb6e1ac73929bb23bca4fd3c79ce44a71","tid":621349,"uid":42629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T18:52:22.000Z","msg":"最緊要有無女濕身"},{"pid":"5a785c2e9cb30a2bf1b80e4bce57fb2dc8381467","tid":621349,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T18:54:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n乜鳩節日/活動都可以商業化    意義在於消費 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}